Platform.Manufacture-Protocol:
PCR product microarray of ORF's from S. Typhimurium LT2, S. Typhimurium SL1344, S. Typhimurium DT104, S. Enteritidis PT4, and S. Gallinarum 287/91. For the description of PCR amplification and printing procedures see:
Clements et al., (2002) PNAS 99(13): 8784-8789;
Nagy et al., (2006) Infect. Immun. 74(10):5914-5925
